{"tid":1745550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新經濟圈地圖指南 Explorit  - 可以公測啦！","createTime":"2019-11-22T09:28:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T22:00:04.000Z","uid":298995,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"588fbb0c60fb2893a02d449ec220fdbf229131c3","tid":1745550,"uid":298995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:28:18.000Z","msg":"經過一連串既瘋狂單機同細規模封測之後，<br />\n即使資料暫時都係包括某幾個區既餐廳為主，<br />\n但係終於過到自已個關覺得可以放得出街。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Explorit 香港新經濟圈地圖指南 ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://app.explorit.co\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp.explorit.co&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=ba5c05e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://app.explorit.co</a><br />\n<br />\n經過 2 - 3 個月單機開發既過程， <br />\n一 直都知道不斷有好多有心同路人士係呢方面出左好力，<br />\n自已亦都有用好幾個，<br />\n但一直都覺得好多位都係 &ldquo;如果有呢樣就好啦&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我就盡量將呢啲功能放係 Explorit 當中： <br />\n<br />\n1. 快速捷徑 - 唔駛諗禁落去就已經可以俾哂過慮好既黃鋪<br />\n2. 支持多重搜尋 - 餐廳分類，18 區地區分類，餐廳名稱分類等等。<br />\n3. 定位功能 - 有啲既快速捷徑係支援搜尋附近 3 公里既鋪頭 <br />\n4. 參考資料處理 - 各大用戶可以提交鋪頭既參考資料，而其他用家可以幫每一個資料投票。 （呢項功能之後會再完善算法，自動計算黃藍相對指標。）<br />\n5. 電腦及手機網頁版均支援 - 由於開發上以基礎為主，所以先以網頁版本出街，亦都為手機上做左有限度既支援。App 會係功能穩定後再開發 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n考慮到資料準確性，暫時提交加新黃鋪都仲係要經過填表格，過後完善用戶系統之後就可以開放已經寫好既內建提交功能。<br />\n<br />\n功能開發上會考慮以 Product Roadmap 形式，稍後會建構公眾都能參興既頁面，供討論、建議，及投票新功能既意向。<br />\n<br />\n至於各同路人，亦歡迎經 IG DM 合作，特別在開放鋪頭資料上，已經準備好初步基礎。<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/explorithk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fexplorithk%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=573fe478\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/explorithk/</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/explorithk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fexplorithk&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=652a1df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/explorithk</a><br />\nTG : 稍後會開 <br />\n由於都係用有限既時間運作 Explorit，回覆如果有延遲請多多見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而 IG/FB 可以先 Follow，現階段會有限度更新。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長遠黎講，<br />\n係想將所有同路人既鋪頭聯繫起來建構黃色經濟圈，然後以平台作基礎架構為黃鋪提供做好生意既便利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要抗爭，真係唔係個個都可以上前線。我希望呢樣可以降低和理非以經濟手段抗爭既門檻。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc661a26822fab052bef278d430fd9cc2ebebcb","tid":1745550,"uid":298995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:45:11.000Z","msg":"知道區選就近,好易沉<br />\n手動推幾下啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03372fa267ef641b59d550bfc474a9b484c2e610","tid":1745550,"uid":298995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:45:55.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"9c8abc659925610853bbf1b233c88e7356dd68a3","tid":1745550,"uid":298995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:46:19.000Z","msg":"推多下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d2e93ce79dca414e8869d7aa23b8f20cf02f25","tid":1745550,"uid":298995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:13:47.000Z","msg":"再推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed73c7d5978b504fd82efd9e5f546ca07a2256a","tid":1745550,"uid":298995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:28:13.000Z","msg":"自推 PISH"},{"pid":"6e9ad23e2da9e96cd94b6c4e564b6bb5d6793123","tid":1745550,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a3f46b4b1ab0cb