-27T16:22:41.000Z","msg":"同hk-restart黃藍食店係咪overlap咗?"},{"pid":"c00690af8e9c51c1b0df057d982373a48e4043c8","tid":1745550,"uid":35216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T18:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e44efb2ddc88fb3ed0a0ca3f8959a91b97dc0ee","tid":1745550,"uid":274542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T18:39:59.000Z","msg":"可唔可以剷走啲仲播cctvb嘅所謂黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969b11511f7c3bef427edbda2835bd462a498e01","tid":1745550,"uid":298995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T20:07:41.000Z","msg":"我一次過回覆啦<br />\n<br />\n1. 有無機會變成 Opensource<br />\n有機會做到，<br />\n本身而家呢隻 Web 係定位做 Prototype，<br />\n所以入面有好多係 Structure 唔夠好既 Code。<br />\n原本計畫係用 Web 先寫相關功能，再之後寫 App 一次 Restructure。 <br />\n<br />\n2. 諗緊有無咩方法可以 Sustain 到呢類 Services <br />\n真心講，如果真係要做起黃色經濟圈，入面既每一環都真係要 Self-sustain 先行得遠。<br />\n你見我多數都係凌晨 3，4 點先覆到 PO 就知咩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 同其他 Overlap 左<br />\n係資料上會係，但功能上會有唔同，<br />\n例如一啲細分類就要自已做埋，一開Site 既捷徑等等，都係我自己一路用緊其他工具既時候覺得不足既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家講黃藍店既多數都係由 Whatsgap, Restart, 黃藍店既資料出黎。<br />\n（有時見到唔齊我地都會自已上網再搵齊佢... ）<br />\n<br />\n4. 可唔可以剷走&quot;偽黃店&quot; <br />\n而家寫緊一個黃藍指標既基制出黎，要啲時間，<br />\n而家可以理解為用戶可以為鋪頭既黃藍資料評分。<br />\n暫時會以黃藍地圖資料作基礎加入各區黃鋪，如果你見到有啲鋪頭真係唔應該出現既，可以經返報料表格報返俾我地聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（個人睇法係：如果佢播CCTVB 係指住佢黎鬧既話...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n<br />\n大家唔好俾佢停，<br />\n繼續懲罰黃鋪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd648559e007ec31ed294b3c3db228bc5e6d499","tid":1745550,"uid":298995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db48b29b316782e1e54bd9b55cc3736201f8aaf7","tid":1745550,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T19:44:33.000Z","msg":"用左幾分鐘<br />\n1. 會唔會將好多舖頭分錯類<br />\n2. 我求其用「茶記」分類睇太子旺角<br />\n    D茶舍、外賣壽司店都歸左「茶記」類, 我剩係想坐低食快餐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 用ANDROID機按返回鍵變左直接上一個網頁, 逼住搵番網頁既「返  回」鍵<br />\n4. 按完「茶記」分類唔識轉番定位附近既地圖, 要人手拉番地圖<br />\n5. LOAD慢左D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用「茶記」、「飲品」、「麵」分類係幾好, 可惜資料準確性唔高<br />\n等你整好再推過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T16:11:31.000Z","msg":"5 <br />\n岩岩做多左啲功夫，而家 Loading 快左好多 🙇🏻&zwj;♂️"}]}